trans-unit.source: The mouseleave event is fired when a pointing device (usually a mouse) is moved off the element that has the listener attached.
trans-unit.target: 的 mouseleave 当指向设备（通常为小鼠）移离贴有侦听器元件事件被触发。

trans-unit.source: The mousemove event is raised when the user moves the mouse.
trans-unit.target: 的 mousemove ，当用户移动鼠标事件被引发。

trans-unit.source: The mozFrameBufferLength property can be set to a new value for lower latency, larger amounts of data, etc. The size given must be a number between 512 and 16384. Using any other size results in an exception being thrown. The best time to set a new length is after the loadedmetadata event fires, when the audio info is known, but before the audio has started or MozAudioAvailable events have begun firing.
trans-unit.target: 该 mozFrameBufferLength 属性可以被设置为一个新的值用于低等待时间，更大量的数据，等等给出的尺寸必须是512和16384之间的数使用任何其它尺寸导致抛出异常。设置新长度的最佳时间是在知道音频信息的情况下，在loadmetadata事件触发后，但在音频开始或 MozAudioAvailable 事件开始触发之前，设置新的长度。

trans-unit.source: The multiEntry read-only property of the IDBIndex interface returns a boolean value that affects how the index behaves when the result of evaluating the index's key path yields an array.
trans-unit.target: IDBIndex 接口的 multiEntry 只读属性返回一个布尔值，当评估索引键路径的结果产生一个数组时，该布尔值会影响索引的行为。

trans-unit.source: The muted read-only property of the MediaStreamTrack interface returns a Boolean value indicating whether or not the track is currently unable to provide media output.
trans-unit.target: MediaStreamTrack 接口的已 muted 只读属性返回一个 Boolean 值，该布尔值指示轨道当前是否无法提供媒体输出。

trans-unit.source: The myArray.myMethod function is passed to setTimeout, then when it's called, its this is not set so it defaults to the window object. There's also no option to pass a thisArg to setTimeout as there is in Array methods like forEach, reduce, etc. and as shown below, using call to set this doesn't work either.
trans-unit.target: 该 myArray.myMethod 函数传递到 setTimeout 的，那么当它的名字，它的 this 没有设置，因此默认为 window 对象。也没有将 thisArg 传递给setTimeout的选项，因为像forEach，reduce等Array方法中一样，并且如下所示，使用 call 来设置 this 也不起作用。

trans-unit.source: The nackCount property of the RTCRtpStreamStats dictionary is a numeric value indicating the number of times the receiver sent a NACK packet to the sender. A NACK (Negative ACKnowledgement, also called "Generic NACK") packet tells the sender that one or more of the RTP packets it sent were lost in transport.
trans-unit.target: RTCRtpStreamStats 词典的 nackCount 属性是一个数字值，指示接收方向发送方发送NACK数据包的次数。 NACK（负确认，也称为“通用NACK”）数据包告诉发送方它发送的一个或多个RTP数据包在传输中丢失。

trans-unit.source: The name property of the Credential interface returns a DOMString, containing the name associated with a credential. It should be a human-readable, public name.
trans-unit.target: Credential 接口的 name 属性返回一个 DOMString ，其中包含与凭据关联的名称。它应该是人类可读的公共名称。

trans-unit.source: The name property of the HTMLSlotElement interface returns or sets the slot name. A slot is a placeholder inside a web component that users can fill with their own markup.
trans-unit.target: HTMLSlotElement 接口的 name 属性返回或设置插槽名称。插槽是Web组件内的占位符，用户可以使用自己的标记来填充。

trans-unit.source: The name property of the IDBIndex interface contains a string which names the index.
trans-unit.target: IDBIndex 接口的 name 属性包含一个为索引命名的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The name property of the IDBObjectStore interface indicates the name of this object store.
trans-unit.target: IDBObjectStore 接口的 name 属性指示此对象库的名称。

trans-unit.source: The name property of the PerformanceEntry interface returns a value that further specifies the value returned by the PerformanceEntry.entryType property. This property is read only.
trans-unit.target: PerformanceEntry 接口的 name 属性返回一个值，该值进一步指定 PerformanceEntry.entryType 属性返回的值。该属性是只读的。

trans-unit.source: The name read-only property of the DOMException interface returns a DOMString that contains one of the strings associated with an error name.
trans-unit.target: DOMException 接口的 name 只读属性返回一个 DOMString ，其中包含与错误name相关联的字符串之一。

trans-unit.source: The name read-only property of the Lock interface returns the name passed to LockManager.request selected when the lock was requested.
trans-unit.target: Lock 接口的 name 只读属性返回在请求锁定时传递给 LockManager.request 的名称。

trans-unit.source: The name read-only property of the PasswordCredential interface returns a USVSTring containing a human-readable public name for display in a credential chooser.
trans-unit.target: PasswordCredential 接口的 name 只读属性返回 USVSTring ，该USVSTring包含人类可读的公共名称，以在凭证选择器中显示。

trans-unit.source: The name read-only property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface returns the name associated with certain types of events occuring as the SpeechSynthesisUtterance.text is being spoken: the name of the SSML marker reached in the case of a mark event, or the type of boundary reached in the case of a boundary event.
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口的 name 只读属性返回与 SpeechSynthesisUtterance.text 时发生的某些事件类型相关联的名称：如果发生 mark 事件，则到达SSML标记的名称，或者到达边界的类型在 boundary 事件的情况下。

trans-unit.source: The name read-only property of the IDBDatabase interface is a DOMString that contains the name of the connected database.
trans-unit.target: IDBDatabase 接口的 name 只读属性是 DOMString ，其中包含连接的数据库的名称。

trans-unit.source: The name read-only property returns a DOMString value of the server-specified metric name.
trans-unit.target: 该 name 只读属性返回一个 DOMString 服务器指定的度量标准名称的价值。

trans-unit.source: The navigate() method of the WindowClient interface loads a specified URL into a controlled client page then returns a Promise that resolves to the existing WindowClient.
trans-unit.target: 该 navigate() 的方法 WindowClient 接口负载指定的URL为控制客户端页面，然后返回一个 Promise 能解决现有 WindowClient 。

trans-unit.source: The navigationPreload read-only property of the FetchEvent interface returns a Promise that resolves to the instance of NavigationPreloadManager associated with the current service worker registration.
trans-unit.target: FetchEvent 接口的 navigationPreload 只读属性返回一个 Promise ，该Promise解析为与当前服务工作程序注册关联的 NavigationPreloadManager 实例。

trans-unit.source: The navigationPreload read-only property of the ServiceWorkerRegistration interface returns the NavigationPreloadManager associated with the current service worker registration.
trans-unit.target: ServiceWorkerRegistration 接口的 navigationPreload 只读属性返回与当前服务工作者注册关联的 NavigationPreloadManager 。

trans-unit.source: The navigator.webdriver property is true when in:
trans-unit.target: 该 navigator. webdriver 属性为true：

trans-unit.source: The navigator.onLine attribute must return false if the user agent will not contact the network when the user follows links or when a script requests a remote page (or knows that such an attempt would fail)...
trans-unit.target: 该 navigator.onLine 属性必须返回false，如果用户遵循链接时，或当脚本请求远程页面（或者知道这种尝试会失败）用户代理不会接触网络...

trans-unit.source: The near property tell if there is an object close to the device (true) or not (false).
trans-unit.target: 在 near 属性告诉我们，如果有物体靠近设备（ true ，否则为 false ）。

trans-unit.source: The newVersion read-only property of the IDBVersionChangeEvent interface returns the new version number of the database.
trans-unit.target: IDBVersionChangeEvent 接口的 newVersion 只读属性返回数据库的新版本号。

trans-unit.source: The nextHopProtocol read-only property is a string representing the network protocol used to fetch the resource, as identified by the ALPN Protocol ID (RFC7301).
trans-unit.target: 所述 nextHopProtocol 只读属性是一个 string 表示网络协议用于获取资源，所确定的ALPN协议ID（RFC7301） 。

trans-unit.source: The nodeType property can be used to distinguish different kind of nodes, such that elements, text and comments, from each other.
trans-unit.target: 该 nodeType 属性可被用于区分不同类型的节点，以使得 elements ， text 和 comments ，从对方。

trans-unit.source: The noiseSuppression cconstraint indicates whether or not the browser offers the ability to automatically control the gain (volume) on media tracks; this obviously is contingent on whether or not the individual device supports automatic gain control as well.
trans-unit.target: 该 noiseSuppression cconstraint表示是否浏览器提供自动控制在媒体轨道增益（体积比）的能力; 显然，这取决于单个设备是否也支持自动增益控制。

trans-unit.source: The nonce property of the HTMLElement interface returns the cryptographic number used once that is used by Content Security Policy to determine whether a given fetch will be allowed to proceed.
trans-unit.target: HTMLElement 接口的 nonce 属性返回一次使用的密码，该密码由内容安全策略用于确定是否将允许进行给定的提取。

trans-unit.source: The normalize() method has been modified so that Text node can also be normalized if the proper DOMConfiguration flag is set.
trans-unit.target: 的 normalize() 方法已被修改，使得 Text ，如果适当的节点也可以被归一化 DOMConfiguration 标志被设置。

trans-unit.source: The normalize() method has been moved to Node.
trans-unit.target: 的 normalize() 方法已经被移动到 Node 。

trans-unit.source: The normalize property of the ConvolverNode interface is a boolean that controls whether the impulse response from the buffer will be scaled by an equal-power normalization when the buffer attribute is set, or not.
trans-unit.target: ConvolverNode 接口的 normalize 属性是一个布尔值，它控制是否在设置 buffer 属性时用等幂归一化来缩放来自缓冲区的冲激响应。

trans-unit.source: The noteReleased() function is the event handler called when the user releases the mouse button or moves the mouse out of the key that's currently playing.
trans-unit.target: 该 noteReleased() 函数调用该事件处理程序，当用户释放鼠标按键或鼠标移出，因此目前起着关键的。

trans-unit.source: The notification read-only property of the NotificationEvent interface returns the instance of the Notification that was clicked to fire the event. The Notification provides read-only access to many properties that were set at the instantiation time of the Notification such as tag and data attributes that allow you to store information for defered use in the notificationclick event.
trans-unit.target: 该 notification 只读财产 NotificationEvent 接口返回的情况下 Notification 说被点击触发事件。该 Notification 提供只读到设定在通知的实例化时，例如，许多属性和访问 tag 和 data 属性，让您存储信息在DEFERED使用 notificationclick 事件。

trans-unit.source: The numberOfChannels property of the AudioBuffer interface returns an integer representing the number of discrete audio channels described by the PCM data stored in the buffer.
trans-unit.target: AudioBuffer 接口的 numberOfChannels 属性返回一个整数，该整数表示由存储在缓冲区中的PCM数据描述的离散音频通道的数量。

trans-unit.source: The numberOfInputs property of the AudioNode interface returns the number of inputs feeding the node. Source nodes are defined as nodes having a numberOfInputs property with a value of 0.
trans-unit.target: AudioNode 接口的 numberOfInputs 属性返回输入节点的输入数。源节点被定义为具有 numberOfInputs 属性且值为0的节点。

trans-unit.source: The numberOfOutputs property of the AudioNode interface returns the number of outputs coming out of the node. Destination nodes — like AudioDestinationNode — have a value of 0 for this attribute.
trans-unit.target: AudioNode 接口的 numberOfOutputs 属性返回从节点出来的输出数量。目的节点（例如 AudioDestinationNode )的此属性值为0。

trans-unit.source: The objectStore() method of the IDBTransaction interface returns an object store that has already been added to the scope of this transaction.
trans-unit.target: IDBTransaction 接口的 objectStore() 方法返回一个已添加到此事务范围内的对象存储。

trans-unit.source: The objectStore property of the IDBIndex interface returns the name of the object store referenced by the current index.
trans-unit.target: IDBIndex 接口的 objectStore 属性返回当前索引引用的对象存储的名称。

trans-unit.source: The objectStoreNames read-only property of the IDBDatabase interface is a DOMStringList containing a list of the names of the object stores currently in the connected database.
trans-unit.target: IDBDatabase 接口的 objectStoreNames 只读属性是 DOMStringList ,其中包含当前在连接的数据库中的对象存储的名称的列表。

trans-unit.source: The objectStoreNames read-only property of the IDBTransaction interface returns a DOMStringList of names of IDBObjectStore objects.
trans-unit.target: IDBTransaction 接口的 objectStoreNames 只读属性返回 IDBObjectStore 对象名称的 DOMStringList 。

trans-unit.source: The observe() method of the PerformanceObserver interface is used to specify the set of performance entry types to observe. The performance entry types are specified as an array of DOMString objects, each naming one entry type; the type names are documented in Performance entry type names in PerformanceEntry.entryType.
trans-unit.target: PerformanceObserver 接口的 observe() 方法用于指定要观察的性能条目类型集。性能条目类型被指定为 DOMString 对象的数组，每个对象都命名一种条目类型。类型名称都记录在性能条目类型名称中PerformanceEntry.entryType。

trans-unit.source: The offset argument is optional.
trans-unit.target: 该 offset 参数可选。

trans-unit.source: The offset read-only property of the VREyeParameters interface
trans-unit.target: VREyeParameters 接口的 offset 只读属性

trans-unit.source: The offsetLeft read-only property of the VisualViewport interface returns the offset of the left edge of the visual viewport from the left edge of the layout viewport in CSS pixels.
trans-unit.target: VisualViewport 接口的 offsetLeft 只读属性返回视觉视口的左边缘相对于布局视口的左边缘以CSS像素为单位的偏移量。

trans-unit.source: The offsetTop read-only property of the VisualViewport interface returns the offset of the top edge of the visual viewport from the top edge of the layout viewport in CSS pixels.
trans-unit.target: VisualViewport 接口的 offsetTop 只读属性返回视觉视口的顶部边缘与布局视口的顶部边缘之间的偏移量（以CSS像素为单位）。

trans-unit.source: The offsetX read-only property of the MouseEvent interface provides the offset in the X coordinate of the mouse pointer between that event and the padding edge of the target node.
trans-unit.target: MouseEvent 接口的 offsetX 只读属性提供该事件与目标节点的填充边缘之间鼠标指针X坐标的偏移量。

trans-unit.source: The offsetY read-only property of the MouseEvent interface provides the offset in the Y coordinate of the mouse pointer between that event and the padding edge of the target node.
trans-unit.target: MouseEvent 接口的 offsetY 只读属性提供该事件与目标节点的填充边缘之间鼠标指针的Y坐标中的偏移量。

trans-unit.source: The oldVersion read-only property of the IDBVersionChangeEvent interface returns the old version number of the database.
trans-unit.target: IDBVersionChangeEvent 接口的 oldVersion 只读属性返回数据库的旧版本号。

trans-unit.source: The onabort event handler of the IDBTransaction interface handles the abort event, fired, when the current transaction is aborted via the IDBTransaction.abort method.
trans-unit.target: 当当前事务通过 IDBTransaction.abort 方法中止时， IDBTransaction 接口的 onabort 事件处理程序处理触发的中止事件。

trans-unit.source: The onabort read-only property of the FetchSignal interface is an event handler Invoked when an abort event fires, i.e. when the fetch request(s) the signal is communicating with is/are aborted.
trans-unit.target: FetchSignal 接口的 onabort 只读属性是事件处理程序，该事件处理程序在 abort 事件触发时（即，在与信号进行通信的读取请求时）异常中止时调用。

trans-unit.source: The onactivateEventHandler is called when one of the Sensor interface's child interfaces becomes active.
trans-unit.target: 该 onactivate EventHandler ，当传感器接口的子接口中的一个被激活时调用。

trans-unit.source: The onaudioend property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when the user agent has finished capturing audio (when the audioend event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 所述 onaudioend 所述的属性 SpeechRecognition 接口表示的事件处理程序，当用户代理具有完成捕获的音频，将运行（在时 audioend 事件触发）。

trans-unit.source: The onaudioprocess event handler of the ScriptProcessorNode interface represents the EventHandler to be called for the audioprocess event that is dispatched to ScriptProcessorNode node types. An event of type AudioProcessingEvent will be dispatched to the event handler.
trans-unit.target: ScriptProcessorNode 接口的 onaudioprocess 事件处理程序表示要为分配给 ScriptProcessorNode 节点类型的 audioprocess 事件调用的 EventHandler 。类型 AudioProcessingEvent 的事件将分派给事件处理程序。

trans-unit.source: The onaudiostart property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when the user agent has started to capture audio (when the audiostart event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onaudiostart 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序，当用户代理已经开始捕获音频，将运行（在当 audiostart 事件触发。）

trans-unit.source: The onblocked event handler of the IDBOpenDBRequest interface is the event handler for the blocked event. This event is triggered when the upgradeneeded should be triggered because of a version change but the database is still in use (that is, not closed) somewhere, even after the versionchange event was sent.
trans-unit.target: 所述 onblocked 所述的事件处理程序 IDBOpenDBRequest 接口是事件处理程序 blocked 事件。当由于版本更改而触发 upgradeneeded 需要触发该事件时，即使在发送了 versionchange 事件之后，仍在某个地方使用数据库（即未关闭），也会触发此事件。

trans-unit.source: The onboundary property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface represents an event handler that will run when the spoken utterance reaches a word or sentence boundary (when the boundary event fires.)
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口的 onboundary 属性表示一个事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在语音到达单词或句子的边界时触发（当 boundary 事件触发时）。

trans-unit.source: The oncanplay property sets and returns the event handler for the canplay event.
trans-unit.target: 该 oncanplay 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 canplay 事件。

trans-unit.source: The oncanplaythrough property sets and returns the event handler for the canplaythrough event.
trans-unit.target: 该 oncanplaythrough 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 canplaythrough 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onchange property of the ScreenOrientation is an event handler fired whenever is the EventHandler called when the screen changes orientation.
trans-unit.target: ScreenOrientation 的 onchange 属性是一个事件处理程序，该事件处理程序在屏幕更改方向时调用 EventHandler 时触发。

trans-unit.source: The onchange property sets and returns the event handler for the change event.
trans-unit.target: 该 onchange 特性集和回报的事件处理程序的 change 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onclick property of the Notification interface specifies an event listener to receive click events. These events occur when the user clicks on a displayed Notification.
trans-unit.target: Notification 接口的 onclick 属性指定一个事件侦听器，以接收 click 事件。这些事件在用户单击显示的 Notification 时发生。

trans-unit.source: The onclose event handler of the IDBDatabase interface handles the close event, which is fired when the database is unexpectedly closed. This can happen, for example, when the application is shut down or access to the disk the database is stored on is lost while the database is open.
trans-unit.target: IDBDatabase 接口的 onclose 事件处理程序处理 close 事件，该事件在数据库意外关闭时触发。例如，当应用程序关闭或打开数据库时，丢失了对存储数据库的磁盘的访问时，可能会发生这种情况。

trans-unit.source: The onclose property of the Notification interface specifies an event listener to receive close events. These events occur when a Notification is closed.
trans-unit.target: Notification 接口的 onclose 属性指定一个事件侦听器以接收 close 事件。这些事件在 Notification 关闭时发生。

trans-unit.source: The onclose property of the WorkerGlobalScope interface represents an EventHandler to be called when the close event occurs and bubbles through the Worker.
trans-unit.target: WorkerGlobalScope 接口的 onclose 属性表示一个 EventHandler ，该事件将在 close 事件发生并通过 Worker 冒泡时被调用。

trans-unit.source: The oncomplete event handler of the IDBTransaction interface handles the complete event, fired when the transaction successfully completes.
trans-unit.target: IDBTransaction 接口的 oncomplete 事件处理程序处理完成事件，该事件在事务成功完成时触发。

trans-unit.source: The oncomplete event handler of the OfflineAudioContext interface is called when the audio processing is terminated, that is when the complete event (of type OfflineAudioCompletionEvent) is raised.
trans-unit.target: 音频处理终止时，即引发 complete 事件（类型为 OfflineAudioCompletionEvent ）时，将调用 OfflineAudioContext 接口的 oncomplete 事件处理程序。

trans-unit.source: The onconnect property of the USB interface is an event handler called whenever a paired device is connected.
trans-unit.target: USB 接口的 onconnect 属性是一个事件处理程序，只要连接了配对的设备，该事件处理程序就会被调用。

trans-unit.source: The oncuechange property sets and returns the event handler for the cuechange event.
trans-unit.target: 该 oncuechange 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 cuechange 事件。

trans-unit.source: The ondisconnect property of the USB is an event handler called whenever a paired device is disconnected.
trans-unit.target: USB 的 ondisconnect 属性是一个事件处理程序，每当配对的设备断开连接时，就会调用该事件处理程序。

trans-unit.source: The ondurationchange property sets and returns the event handler for the durationchange event.
trans-unit.target: 该 ondurationchange 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 durationchange 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onemptied property sets and returns the event handler for the emptied event.
trans-unit.target: 该 onemptied 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序为 emptied 的事件。

trans-unit.source: The onencrypted property of the HTMLMediaElement is an event handler, fired whenever an encrypted event occurs, denoting the media is encrypted.
trans-unit.target: HTMLMediaElement 的 onencrypted 属性是一个事件处理程序，只要发生 encrypted 事件就触发，表示媒体已加密。

trans-unit.source: The onend property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when the speech recognition service has disconnected (when the end event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onend 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序时，语音识别服务已断开，将运行（在当 end 事件触发。）

trans-unit.source: The onend property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface represents an event handler that will run when the utterance has finished being spoken (when the end event fires.)
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口的 onend 属性表示一个事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在说完语音后（在触发 end 事件时）运行。

trans-unit.source: The onended event handler for the AudioScheduledSourceNode interface specifies an EventHandler to be executed when the ended event occurs on the node. This event is sent to the node when the concrete interface (such as AudioBufferSourceNode, OscillatorNode, or ConstantSourceNode) determines that it has stopped playing.
trans-unit.target: AudioScheduledSourceNode 接口的 onended 事件处理程序指定在节点上发生 ended 事件时要执行的 EventHandler 。当具体接口（例如 AudioBufferSourceNode ， OscillatorNode 或 ConstantSourceNode ）确定已停止播放时，将此事件发送到节点。

trans-unit.source: The onended property of the OscillatorNode interface is used to set the event handler for the ended event, which fires when the tone has stopped playing.
trans-unit.target: OscillatorNode 接口的 onended 属性用于设置end事件的事件处理程序，该事件处理程序在音调停止播放时触发。

trans-unit.source: The onended property sets and returns the event handler for the ended event.
trans-unit.target: 该 onended 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 ended 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onerror event handler of the IDBRequest interface handles the error event, fired when a request returns an error.
trans-unit.target: IDBRequest 接口的 onerror 事件处理程序处理 error 事件，该错误事件在请求返回错误时触发。

trans-unit.source: The onerror property of the HTMLMediaElement interface specifies an event listener function which will receive error events sent to the media element. These events occur when some form of error occurs while attempting to load or perform the media.
trans-unit.target: HTMLMediaElement 接口的 onerror 属性指定事件侦听器函数，该函数将接收发送到media元素的 error 事件。当尝试加载或执行媒体时发生某种形式的错误时，就会发生这些事件。

trans-unit.source: The onerror property of the Notification interface specifies an event listener to receive error events. These events occur when something goes wrong with a Notification (in many cases an error preventing the notification from being displayed.)
trans-unit.target: Notification 接口的 onerror 属性指定一个事件侦听器以接收 error 事件。当 Notification 发生问题时会发生这些事件（在许多情况下，该错误会阻止显示通知。）

trans-unit.source: The onerror property of the ServiceWorkerContainer interface is an event handler fired whenever an error event occurs in the associated service workers.
trans-unit.target: ServiceWorkerContainer 接口的 onerror 属性是一个事件处理程序，只要在关联的服务工作程序中发生 error 事件，就会触发该事件处理程序。

trans-unit.source: The onerror property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when a speech recognition error occurs (when the error event fires.)
trans-unit.target: SpeechRecognition 接口的 onerror 属性表示事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在语音识别错误发生时（错误事件触发时）运行。

trans-unit.source: The onerror property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface represents an event handler that will run when an error occurs that prevents the utterance from being succesfully spoken (when the error event fires.)
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口的 onerror 属性表示一个事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在发生错误时运行，以防止成功说出话语（在 error 事件触发时）。

trans-unit.source: The onerror property of the WorkerGlobalScope interface represents an EventHandler to be called when the error event occurs and bubbles through the Worker.
trans-unit.target: WorkerGlobalScope 接口的 onerror 属性表示发生 error 事件并在 Worker 中冒泡时要调用的 EventHandler 。

trans-unit.source: The onerrorEventHandler is called when an error occurs on one of the child interfaces of the Sensor interface.
trans-unit.target: 该 onerror 的 EventHandler 时，在的子接口中的一个出现错误被称为 Sensor 接口。

trans-unit.source: The ongoingTouchIndexById() function below scans through the ongoingTouches array to find the touch matching the given identifier, then returns that touch's index into the array.
trans-unit.target: 下面的 ongoingTouchIndexById() 函数将 ongoingTouches 数组，以找到与给定标识符匹配的触摸，然后将该触摸的索引返回到数组中。

trans-unit.source: The ongotpointercaptureEventHandler property of the GlobalEventHandlers interface returns the event handler (function) for the gotpointercapture event type.
trans-unit.target: GlobalEventHandlers 接口的 ongotpointercapture EventHandler 属性返回 gotpointercapture 事件类型的事件处理程序（函数）。

trans-unit.source: The oninvalid property sets and returns the event handler for the invalid event.
trans-unit.target: 该 oninvalid 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序为 invalid 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onkeystatuseschange property of the MediaKeySession is an event handler, fired whenever a keystatuschange event ocurrs, denoting there has been a change in the keys or their statuses within a session.
trans-unit.target: 该 onkeystatuseschange 的财产 MediaKeySession 是事件处理程序，发射每当 keystatuschange 事件ocurrs，表示出现了一个会话中键或他们的状态的变化。

trans-unit.source: The onlanguagechange property of the WorkerGlobalScope interface represents an EventHandler to be called when the languagechange event occurs and bubbles through the Worker.
trans-unit.target: WorkerGlobalScope 接口的 onlanguagechange 属性表示在发生 languagechange 事件并在 Worker 中冒泡时要调用的 EventHandler 。

trans-unit.source: The onload property of the GlobalEventHandlers mixin is an event handler for the load event of a Window, XMLHttpRequest, <img> element, etc., which fires when the resource has loaded.
trans-unit.target: 所述 onload 所述的属性 GlobalEventHandlers 混入是用于一个事件处理程序 load 事件 a的 Window ， XMLHttpRequest 的， <img> 元件等，当资源已经加载哪个火灾。

trans-unit.source: The onloadeddata property sets and returns the event handler for the loadeddata event.
trans-unit.target: 该 onloadeddata 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 loadeddata 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onloadedmetadata property sets and returns the event handler for the loadedmetadata event.
trans-unit.target: 该 onloadedmetadata 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 loadedmetadata 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onloadend property of the GlobalEventHandlers mixin is an EventHandler representing the code to be called when the loadend event is raised (when progress has stopped on the loading of a resource.)
trans-unit.target: GlobalEventHandlers mixin 的 onloadend 属性是一个 EventHandler ,表示引发 loadend 事件时（资源加载进度停止时）要调用的代码。

trans-unit.source: The onloadstart property of the GlobalEventHandlers mixin is an EventHandler representing the code to be called when the loadstart event is raised (when progress has begun on the loading of a resource.)
trans-unit.target: GlobalEventHandlers mixin 的 onloadstart 属性是一个 EventHandler ,表示引发 loadstart 事件时（资源加载开始时）要调用的代码。

trans-unit.source: The onlostpointercaptureEventHandler property of the GlobalEventHandlers interface returns the event handler (function) for the lostpointercapture event type.
trans-unit.target: GlobalEventHandlers 接口的 onlostpointercapture EventHandler 属性返回 lostpointercapture 事件类型的事件处理程序（函数）。

trans-unit.source: The only() method of the IDBKeyRange interface creates a new key range containing a single value.
trans-unit.target: IDBKeyRange 接口的 only() 方法创建一个包含单个值的新键范围。

trans-unit.source: The onmark property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface represents an event handler that will run when the spoken utterance reaches a named SSML mark tag (when the mark event fires.)
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口的 onmark 属性表示事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在语音到达命名的SSML标记标签时（在 mark 事件触发时）运行。

trans-unit.source: The onmessage handler allows us to run some code whenever a message is received, with the message itself being available in the message event's data attribute. Here we simply multiply together the two numbers then use postMessage() again, to post the result back to the main thread.
trans-unit.target: 该 onmessage 处理程序允许我们运行只要接收到消息的一些代码，与正在可用信息本身 message 事件的 data 属性。在这里，我们简单地将两个数字相乘，然后再次使用 postMessage() 将结果发布回主线程。

trans-unit.source: The onmessage property of the DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope interface represents an EventHandler to be called when the message event occurs and bubbles through the Worker — i.e. when a message is sent to the worker using the Worker.postMessage method.
trans-unit.target: DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope 接口的 onmessage 属性表示发生 message 事件并通过 Worker 冒泡时（即，使用 Worker.postMessage 方法将消息发送给Worker时）要调用的 EventHandler 。

trans-unit.source: The onmessage property of the MediaKeySession is an event handler, fired whenever a MediaKeyMessageEvent ocurrs, denoting a message is generated by the content decryption module.
trans-unit.target: MediaKeySession 的 onmessage 属性是一个事件处理程序，每当出现 MediaKeyMessageEvent 时触发，表示内容解密模块生成了一条消息。

trans-unit.source: The onmessage property of the ServiceWorkerContainer interface is an event handler fired whenever a message event occurs — when incoming messages are received to the ServiceWorkerContainer object (e.g., via a MessagePort.postMessage() call).
trans-unit.target: ServiceWorkerContainer 接口的 onmessage 属性是 message 事件发生时触发的事件处理程序—当收到传入的消息到 ServiceWorkerContainer 对象时（例如，通过 MessagePort.postMessage() 调用）。

trans-unit.source: The onmessage property of the WindowEventHandlers is the EventHandler called whenever an object receives a message event.
trans-unit.target: WindowEventHandlers 的 onmessage 属性是在对象收到 message 事件时调用的 EventHandler 。

trans-unit.source: The onmessage property of the Worker interface represents an EventHandler, that is a function to be called when the message event occurs. These events are of type MessageEvent and will be called when the worker's parent receives a message (i.e. from the DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope.postMessage method.
trans-unit.target: Worker 接口的 onmessage 属性表示 EventHandler ，它是发生 message 事件时要调用的函数。这些事件的类型为 MessageEvent ,并且在工作人员的父级收到消息时（即从 DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope.postMessage 方法接收）将被调用。

trans-unit.source: The onmousedown property returns the onmousedown event handler code on the current element.
trans-unit.target: 该 onmousedown 事件属性返回 onmousedown 事件目前的元素上的事件处理程序代码。

trans-unit.source: The onmouseenter property sets and returns the event handler for the mouseenter event.
trans-unit.target: 该 onmouseenter 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 mouseenter 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onmouseleave property sets and returns the event handler for the mouseleave event.
trans-unit.target: 该 onmouseleave 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 mouseleave 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onnomatch property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when the speech recognition service returns a final result with no significant recognition (when the nomatch event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onnomatch 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序时，语音识别服务返回无显著识别最终结果将运行（在当 nomatch 事件触发。）

trans-unit.source: The onoffline property of the WorkerGlobalScope interface represents an EventHandler to be called when the offline event occurs and bubbles through the Worker.
trans-unit.target: WorkerGlobalScope 接口的 onoffline 属性表示当发生 offline 事件并在 Worker 中冒泡时要调用的 EventHandler 。

trans-unit.source: The ononline property of the WorkerGlobalScope interface represents an EventHandler to be called when the online event occurs and bubbles through the Worker.
trans-unit.target: WorkerGlobalScope 接口的 ononline 属性表示一个 EventHandler ，该事件将在 online 事件发生并通过 Worker 冒泡时被调用。

trans-unit.source: The onpause property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface represents an event handler that will run when the utterance is paused part way through (when the pause event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onpause 的财产 SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口代表一个事件处理程序时，话语是通过暂停一部分的方式，将运行时（ pause 事件触发。）

trans-unit.source: The onpause property sets and returns the event handler for the pause event.
trans-unit.target: 该 onpause 属性设置或返回的事件处理程序的 pause 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onreadingEventHandler is called when a reading is taken on one of the child interfaces of the Sensor interface.
trans-unit.target: 该 onreading EventHandler 时，读取读数上的子接口中的一个被称为 Sensor 接口。

trans-unit.source: The onresize event handler of the VisualViewport interface is the EventHandler called when a viewport is resized.
trans-unit.target: 调整视口大小时， VisualViewport 接口的 onresize 事件处理程序为 EventHandler 。

trans-unit.source: The onresourcetimingbufferfull property is an event handler that will be called when the resourcetimingbufferfull event is fired. This event is fired when the browser's resource timing performance buffer is full.
trans-unit.target: 该 onresourcetimingbufferfull 属性是 event handler 时，将调用 resourcetimingbufferfull 事件。当浏览器的资源计时性能缓冲区已满时，将触发此事件。

trans-unit.source: The onresult property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when the speech recognition service returns a result — a word or phrase has been positively recognized and this has been communicated back to the app (when the result event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onresult 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序将运行时的语音识别服务会返回一个结果-一个词或短语已经积极认可，这已经传回给应用程序（在当 result 事件触发。）

trans-unit.source: The onresume property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface represents an event handler that will run when a paused utterance is resumed (when the resume event fires.)
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口的 onresume 属性表示一个事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在恢复暂停的语音时（当 resume 事件触发时）运行。

trans-unit.source: The onscroll event handler of the VisualViewport interface is the EventHandler called when a viewport is scrolled.
trans-unit.target: VisualViewport 接口的 onscroll 事件处理程序是滚动视口时调用的 EventHandler 。

trans-unit.source: The onshippingaddresschange event of the PaymentRequest interface is fired whenever the user changes their shipping address, including when an address is added by the user for the first time.
trans-unit.target: 每当用户更改其收货地址（包括用户首次添加地址）时，都会触发 PaymentRequest 接口的 onshippingaddresschange 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onshippingoptionchange event of the PaymentRequest interface is fired whenever the user changes a shipping option.
trans-unit.target: 每当用户更改送货选项时，都会触发 PaymentRequest 接口的 onshippingoptionchange 事件。

trans-unit.source: The onshow property of the Notification interface specifies an event listener to receive show events. These events occur when a Notification is displayed.
trans-unit.target: Notification 接口的 onshow 属性指定一个事件侦听器以接收 show 事件。这些事件在显示 Notification 时发生。

trans-unit.source: The onsoundend property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when any sound — recognisable speech or not — has stopped being detected (when the soundend event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onsoundend 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序将运行在任何声音-语音识别或不- （的时候已经停止被检测 soundend 。事件触发）

trans-unit.source: The onsoundstart property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when any sound — recognisable speech or not — has been detected (when the soundstart event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onsoundstart 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序时的任何声音，将运行-识别语音与否- （中当检测 soundstart 。事件触发）

trans-unit.source: The onspeechend property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when speech recognised by the speech recognition service has stopped being detected (when the speechend event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onspeechend 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序时的讲话所确认的语音识别服务已停止被检测将运行（在当 speechend 事件触发。）

trans-unit.source: The onspeechstart property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when sound recognised by the speech recognition service as speech has been detected (when the speechstart event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 该 onspeechstart 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序，语音已经检测到的声音所确认的语音识别服务将运行（在当 speechstart 事件触发。）

trans-unit.source: The onstart property of the SpeechRecognition interface represents an event handler that will run when the speech recognition service has begun listening to incoming audio with intent to recognize grammars associated with the current SpeechRecognition (when the start event fires.)
trans-unit.target: 在 onstart 的财产 SpeechRecognition 接口代表一个事件处理程序将运行时的语音识别服务已经开始听意图识别与当前相关的语法输入音频 SpeechRecognition （在当 start 事件触发。）

trans-unit.source: The onstart property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface represents an event handler that will run when the utterance has begun to be spoken (when the start event fires.)
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口的 onstart 属性表示一个事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在开始说出语音时（在 start 事件触发时）运行。

trans-unit.source: The onstatechange property of the BaseAudioContext interface defines an event handler function to be called when the statechange event fires: this occurs when the audio context's state changes.
trans-unit.target: BaseAudioContext 接口的 onstatechange 属性定义一个 statechange 处理程序事件，该事件处理程序函数在statechange事件触发时调用：当音频上下文的状态更改时，将发生此事件。

trans-unit.source: The onsuccess event handler of the IDBRequest interface handles the success event, fired when the result of a request is successfully returned.
trans-unit.target: IDBRequest 接口的 onsuccess 事件处理程序处理 success 事件，该事件在成功返回请求结果时触发。

trans-unit.source: The ontonechange property of the RTCDTMFSender interface is used to set the event handler for the tonechange event, which is sent to the RTCDTMFSender each time a tone begins or ends. The event handler receives as input a single parameter of type RTCDTMFToneChangeEvent, which describes the change.
trans-unit.target: RTCDTMFSender 接口的 ontonechange 属性用于设置 tonechange 事件的事件处理程序，每次音频开始或结束时，该事件处理程序都会发送到 RTCDTMFSender 。事件处理程序接收描述为更改的 RTCDTMFToneChangeEvent 类型的单个参数作为输入。

trans-unit.source: The onupgradeneeded property of the IDBOpenDBRequest interface is the event handler for the upgradeneeded event, triggered when a database of a bigger version number than the existing stored database is loaded.
trans-unit.target: 该 onupgradeneeded 的财产 IDBOpenDBRequest 接口是事件处理程序 upgradeneeded 事件，当被加载比现有的存储数据库中的大版本号的数据库触发。

trans-unit.source: The onversionchange event handler of the IDBDatabase interface handles the versionchange event, fired when a database structure change (IDBOpenDBRequest.onupgradeneeded event or IDBFactory.deleteDatabase) was requested elsewhere (most probably in another window/tab on the same computer).
trans-unit.target: IDBDatabase 接口的 onversionchange 事件处理程序处理版本更改事件，当在其他地方（很可能在同一台计算机的另一个窗口/选项卡中）请求数据库结构更改（ IDBOpenDBRequest.onupgradeneeded 事件或 IDBFactory.deleteDatabase ）时触发。

trans-unit.source: The onvrdisplayactivate property of the Window interface represents an event handler that will run when a display is able to be presented to (when the vrdisplayactivate event fires), for example if an HMD has been moved to bring it out of standby, or woken up by being put on.
trans-unit.target: Window 界面的 onvrdisplayactivate 属性表示事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在能够显示显示时（在 vrdisplayactivate 事件触发时）运行，例如，如果将HMD移至使其退出待机状态，或者被唤醒被戴上。

trans-unit.source: The onvrdisplayblur property of the Window interface represents an event handler that will run when presentation to a display has been paused for some reason by the browser, OS, or VR hardware (when the vrdisplayblur event fires) — for example, while the user is interacting with a system menu or browser, to prevent tracking or loss of experience.
trans-unit.target: Window 界面的 onvrdisplayblur 属性表示事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在浏览器，OS或VR硬件出于某种原因（当触发 vrdisplayblur 事件时）暂停对显示的演示时运行（例如，当用户进行交互时）与系统菜单或浏览器配合使用，以防止跟踪或失​​去体验。

trans-unit.source: The onvrdisplaydeactivate property of the Window interface represents an event handler that will run when a display can no longer be presented to (when the vrdisplaydeactivate event fires), for example if an HMD has gone into standby or sleep mode due to a period of inactivity.
trans-unit.target: Window 界面的 onvrdisplaydeactivate 属性表示一个事件处理程序，它将在不再显示显示时（在触发 vrdisplaydeactivate 事件时）运行，例如，如果HMD由于一段时间不活动而进入待机或睡眠模式。

trans-unit.source: The onvrdisplayfocus property of the Window interface represents an event handler that will run when presentation to a display has resumed after being blurred (when the vrdisplayfocus event fires).
trans-unit.target: Window 接口的 onvrdisplayfocus 属性表示一个事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在模糊显示后（当 vrdisplayfocus 事件触发时）恢复对显示的显示。

trans-unit.source: The onvrdisplaypresentchange property of the Window interface represents an event handler that will run when the presenting state of a VR display changes — i.e. goes from presenting to not presenting, or vice versa (when the vrdisplaypresentchange event fires).
trans-unit.target: Window 接口的 onvrdisplaypresentchange 属性表示一个事件处理程序，该事件处理程序将在VR显示器的呈现状态更改时运行，即从呈现状态变为不呈现状态，反之亦然（当 vrdisplaypresentchange 事件触发时）。

trans-unit.source: The onwaitingforkey property of the HTMLMediaElement is an event handler, fired when a waitingforkey event occurs, when playback is blocked while waiting for an encryption key.
trans-unit.target: HTMLMediaElement 的 onwaitingforkey 属性是一个事件处理程序，在发生 waitingforkey 事件，在等待加密密钥的同时阻止播放时触发。

trans-unit.source: The onwheel property returns the onwheel event handler code on the current element.
trans-unit.target: 该 onwheel 属性返回 onwheel 当前元素上的事件处理程序代码。

trans-unit.source: The open() method creates a new secondary browser window, similar to choosing New Window from the File menu. The strUrl parameter specifies the URL to be fetched and loaded in the new window. If strUrl is an empty string, then a new blank, empty window (URL about:blank) is created with the default toolbars of the main window.
trans-unit.target: 该 open() 方法创建一个新的辅助浏览器窗口，类似于从文件菜单中选择新窗口。该 strUrl 参数指定URL加以取出，并在新窗口中加载。如果 strUrl 是一个空字符串，则将使用主窗口的默认工具栏创建一个新的空白窗口（URL about:blank ）。

trans-unit.source: The open() method of the CacheStorage interface returns a Promise that resolves to the Cache object matching the cacheName.
trans-unit.target: CacheStorage 接口的 open() 方法返回一个 Promise ，该Promise解析为与 cacheName 匹配的 Cache 对象。

trans-unit.source: The open() method of the IDBFactory interface requests opening a connection to a database.
trans-unit.target: IDBFactory 接口的 open() 方法请求打开与数据库的连接。

trans-unit.source: The open() method of the USBDevice interface returns a promise that resolves when a device session has started.
trans-unit.target: USBDevice 接口的 open() 方法返回一个 promise ，该承诺将在设备会话开始时解析。

trans-unit.source: The open property of the HTMLDialogElement interface is a Boolean reflecting the open HTML attribute, indicating whether the dialog is available for interaction.
trans-unit.target: HTMLDialogElement 接口的 open 属性是一个 Boolean 反映了 open HTML属性，指示对话框是否可用于交互。

trans-unit.source: The openCursor() function takes several arguments. First, you can limit the range of items that are retrieved by using a key range object that we'll get to in a minute. Second, you can specify the direction that you want to iterate. In the above example, we're iterating over all objects in ascending order. The success callback for cursors is a little special. The cursor object itself is the result of the request (above we're using the shorthand, so it's event.target.result). Then the actual key and value can be found on the key and value properties of the cursor object. If you want to keep going, then you have to call continue() on the cursor. When you've reached the end of the data (or if there were no entries that matched your openCursor() request) you still get a success callback, but the result property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 该 openCursor() 函数有几个参数。首先，您可以使用我们稍后将要到达的键范围对象来限制所检索项目的范围。其次，您可以指定要迭代的方向。在上面的示例中，我们以升序遍历所有对象。游标的成功回调有些特殊。游标对象本身是请求的 result （在上面，我们使用了简写形式，因此它是 event.target.result ）。然后可以在光标对象的 key 和 value 属性上找到实际的键和值。如果要继续前进，则必须调用 continue() 在光标上。当您到达数据末尾时（或者如果没有与 openCursor() 请求匹配的条目），您仍然会获得成功回调，但是 result 属性是 undefined 。

trans-unit.source: The openCursor() method of the IDBIndex interface returns an IDBRequest object, and, in a separate thread, creates a cursor over the specified key range.

trans-unit.source: The openCursor() method of the IDBObjectStore interface returns an IDBRequest object, and, in a separate thread, returns a new IDBCursorWithValue object. Used for iterating through an object store with a cursor.
trans-unit.target: IDBObjectStore 接口的 openCursor() 方法返回一个 IDBRequest 对象，并在一个单独的线程中返回一个新的 IDBCursorWithValue 对象。用于使用游标遍历对象存储。

trans-unit.source: The openKeyCursor() method of the IDBIndex interface returns an IDBRequest object, and, in a separate thread, creates a cursor over the specified key range, as arranged by this index.
trans-unit.target: IDBIndex 接口的 openKeyCursor() 方法返回一个 IDBRequest 对象，并在一个单独的线程中，在由该索引安排的指定键范围内创建一个游标。

trans-unit.source: The openKeyCursor() method of the IDBObjectStore interface returns an IDBRequest object whose result will be set to an IDBCursor that can be used to iterate through matching results. Used for iterating through the keys of an object store with a cursor.
trans-unit.target: IDBObjectStore 接口的 openKeyCursor() 方法返回一个 IDBRequest 对象，其结果将设置为 IDBCursor ，可用于迭代匹配结果。用于使用游标遍历对象存储的键。

trans-unit.source: The openWindow() method of the Clients interface creates a new top level browsing context and loads a given URL. If the calling script doesn't have permission to show popups, openWindow() will throw an InvalidAccessError.
trans-unit.target: Clients 接口的 openWindow() 方法创建一个新的顶级浏览上下文并加载给定的URL。如果调用脚本没有显示弹出窗口的权限，则 openWindow() 将引发InvalidAccessError。

trans-unit.target: PannerNode 接口的 orientationX 属性指示在3D笛卡尔坐标空间中音频源所面向的方向的X（水平）分量。

trans-unit.target: Element DOM接口的 outerHTML 属性获取描述元素（包括其后代）的序列化HTML片段。也可以设置为将元素替换为从给定字符串解析的节点。

trans-unit.target: AudioContext 接口的 outputLatency 只读属性提供对当前音频上下文的输出延迟的估计。

trans-unit.target: StereoPannerNode 接口的 pan 属性是一个a-rate AudioParam ,代表要应用的平移量。该值的范围是 -1 （左全角）和 1 （右全角）。

trans-unit.target: PannerNode 接口的 panningModel 属性是一个枚举值，用于确定要使用哪种空间化算法将音频定位在3D空间中。

trans-unit.source: The parse() method of the CSSStyleValue interface sets a specific CSS property to the specified values and returns the first value as a CSSStyleValue object.
trans-unit.target: CSSStyleValue 接口的 parse() 方法将特定的CSS属性设置为指定的值，然后将第一个值作为 CSSStyleValue 对象返回。

trans-unit.source: The parseAll() method of the CSSStyleValue interface sets all occurences of a specific CSS property to the specified valueand returns an array of CSSStyleValue objects, each containing one of the supplied values.
trans-unit.target: CSSStyleValue 接口的 parseAll() 方法将特定CSS属性的所有出现都设置为指定的值，并返回 CSSStyleValue 对象的数组，每个对象都包含提供的值之一。

trans-unit.source: The password read-only property of the PasswordCredential interface returns a USVString containing the password of the credential.
trans-unit.target: PasswordCredential 接口的 password 只读属性返回一个 USVString ,其中包含凭据的密码。

This property defaults to 'password', but may be matched to anything your backend service expects.
trans-unit.target: 当通过 fetch 将当前对象提交到远程端点时， PasswordCredential 接口的 passwordName 属性返回一个 USVString ，描述了password字段使用的名称。此属性默认为 'password' ，但可以与您的后端服务期望的任何内容匹配。

trans-unit.source: The pause event is fired when playback has been paused.
trans-unit.target: 在 pause 时播放已暂停事件。

trans-unit.source: The pause event is thrown as a result of the MediaRecorder.pause() method being invoked.
trans-unit.target: 由于调用 MediaRecorder.pause() 方法而引发了 pause 事件。

trans-unit.target: 在 paused 了的只读属性 SpeechSynthesis 接口是一个 Boolean 即返回 true 如果 SpeechSynthesis 对象处于暂停状态，或 false 如果不是。

trans-unit.target: PaymentRequestEvent 接口的 paymentRequestId 只读属性返回 PaymentRequest 对象的ID 。

trans-unit.target: PaymentRequestEvent 接口的 paymentRequestOrigin 只读属性返回初始化 PaymentRequest 对象的来源。

trans-unit.source: The permission read-only property of the Notification interface indicates the current permission granted by the user for the current origin to display web notifications.
trans-unit.target: Notification 界面的 permission 只读属性指示用户为当前来源显示的Web通知授予的当前权限。

trans-unit.source: The permissionState() method of the PushManager interface returns a Promise that resolves to a DOMString indicating the permission state of the push manager. Possible values are 'prompt', 'denied', or 'granted'.
trans-unit.target: PushManager 接口的 permissionState() 方法返回一个 Promise ，该Promise解析为 DOMString ,指示推送管理器的许可状态。可能的值为 'prompt' ， 'denied' 或 'granted' 。

trans-unit.target: StorageManager 接口的 persist() 方法请求使用持久性存储的权限，并返回一个 Promise ，如果已授予许可且框模式为持久性，则该解析为 true ，否则返回 false 。

trans-unit.source: The pipeThrough() method of the ReadableStream interface provides a chainable way of piping the current stream through a transform stream or any other writable/readable pair.
trans-unit.target: ReadableStream 接口的 pipeThrough() 方法提供了一种可链接的方式，通过转换流或任何其他可写/可读对来传递当前流。

trans-unit.target: ReadableStream 接口的 pipeTo() 方法将当前 ReadableStream 通过管道传递给给定的 WritableStream ,并返回一个诺言，该诺言在管道过程成功完成时会实现，或者在遇到任何错误时拒绝。

trans-unit.source: The pitch property of the SpeechSynthesisUtterance interface gets and sets the pitch at which the utterance will be spoken at.
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesisUtterance 接口的 pitch 属性获取并设置说话时的音调。

trans-unit.target: 的 pixels 参数现在接受 ArrayBufferView 类型的 Uint16Array 和 Uint32Array 。

trans-unit.target: 在 playTone() 函数的任务是在给定频率播放提示音。处理程序将使用它来触发键盘上的事件以触发键盘上的相应音调。

trans-unit.target: HTMLIFrameElement 接口的 policy 只读属性返回 Policy 接口，该接口提供了一个简单的API，用于内省应用于特定文档的功能策略。

trans-unit.source: The preventSilentAccess() method of the CredentialsContainer interface sets a flag that specifies whether automatic log in is allowed for future visits to the current origin, then returns an empty Promise. For example, you might call this, after a user signs out of a website to ensure that he/she isn't automatically signed in on the next site visit. Mediation varies by origin, and is an added check point of browser stored credentials, informing a user of an account login status. This method is typically called after a user signs out of a website, ensuring this user's login information is not automatically passed on the next site visit.
trans-unit.target: CredentialsContainer 接口的 preventSilentAccess() 方法设置一个标志，该标志指定是否允许自动登录以供将来访问当前源时使用，然后返回一个空的 Promise 。例如，在用户退出网站以确保他/她在下次访问网站时不会自动登录之后，您可以调用此方法。中介因来源而异，并且是浏览器存储的凭据的附加检查点，用于通知用户帐户登录状态。通常在用户退出网站后调用此方法，以确保在下次访问网站时不会自动传递该用户的登录信息。

trans-unit.source: The setPosition() method of the PannerNode Interface defines the position of the audio source relative to the listener (represented by an AudioListener object stored in the AudioContext.listener attribute.) The three parameters x, y and z are unitless and describe the source's position in 3D space using the right-hand Cartesian coordinate system.
trans-unit.target: PannerNode 接口的 setPosition() 方法定义音频源相对于侦听器的位置（由存储在 AudioContext.listener 属性中的 AudioListener 对象表示。）三个参数 x ， y 和 z 是无单位的，它们描述了源的位置。在3D空间中使用右手笛卡尔坐标系。

trans-unit.source: The setPosition() method's default value of the position is (0,0,0).
trans-unit.target: 所述 setPosition() 方法的位置的缺省值是 (0, 0, 0) 。

trans-unit.source: The setResourceTimingBufferSize() method sets the browser's resource timing buffer size to the specified number of "resource" performance entry type objects.
trans-unit.target: 所述 setResourceTimingBufferSize() 方法设置了浏览器的资源的定时缓冲器大小“指定数目的 resource ” performance entry type 的对象。

trans-unit.source: The setTargetAtTime() method of the AudioParam interface schedules the start of a gradual change to the AudioParam value. This is useful for decay or release portions of ADSR envelopes.
trans-unit.target: AudioParam 接口的 setTargetAtTime() 方法可安排对 AudioParam 值进行逐步更改的开始。这对于ADSR包络的衰减或释放部分很有用。

trans-unit.source: The setTimeout() method of the WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope mixin (and successor to window.setTimeout) sets a timer which executes a function or specified piece of code once after the timer expires.
trans-unit.target: WindowOrWorkerGlobalScope mixin 的 setTimeout() 方法（和window.setTimeout的后继方法）设置一个计时器，该计时器在计时器到期后执行一次功能或指定的代码段。

trans-unit.source: The setValueAtTime() method of the AudioParam interface schedules an instant change to the AudioParam value at a precise time, as measured against AudioContext.currentTime. The new value is given in the value parameter.
trans-unit.target: AudioParam 接口的 setValueAtTime() 方法计划在一个精确的时间对 AudioParam 值进行即时更改，该时间相对于 AudioContext.currentTime 进行了测量。新值在value参数中给出。

trans-unit.source: The setValueCurveAtTime() method of the AudioParam interface schedules the parameter's value to change following a curve defined by a list of values. The curve is a linear interpolation between the sequence of values defined in an array of floating-point values, which are scaled to fit into the given interval starting at startTime and a specific duration.
trans-unit.target: AudioParam 接口的 setValueCurveAtTime() 方法调度参数的值，使其沿着由值列表定义的曲线变化。曲线是在浮点值数组中定义的值序列之间的线性插值，这些值按比例缩放以适合于从 startTime 开始的给定间隔和特定持续时间。

trans-unit.source: The setVelocity() method of the PannerNode Interface defines the velocity vector of the audio source — how fast it is moving and in what direction.
trans-unit.target: PannerNode 接口的 setVelocity() 方法定义了音频源的速度矢量-它的移动速度和方向。

trans-unit.source: The setup() function is responsible for building the keyboard and preparing the app to play music.
trans-unit.target: 该 setup() 函数负责建立键盘和准备的应用程序来播放音乐。

trans-unit.source: The shadowBlur property indicates the size of the blurring effect; this value doesn't correspond to a number of pixels and is not affected by the current transformation matrix. The default value is 0.
trans-unit.target: 所述 shadowBlur 属性指示的模糊效应的大小; 该值不对应于多个像素，并且不受当前变换矩阵的影响。默认值为0。

trans-unit.source: The shadowColor property is a standard CSS color value indicating the color of the shadow effect; by default, it is fully-transparent black.
trans-unit.target: 的 shadowColor 属性是指示的阴影效果的颜色的标准CSS颜色值; 默认情况下，它是完全透明的黑色。

trans-unit.source: The shippingAddress read-only property of the PaymentRequest interface returns the shipping address provided by the user. It is null by default.
trans-unit.target: PaymentRequest 接口的 shippingAddress 只读属性返回用户提供的送货地址。默认情况下为 null 。

trans-unit.source: The shippingAddress read-only property of the PaymentRequest interface returns a PaymentAddress object containing the shipping address provided by the user.
trans-unit.target: PaymentRequest 接口的 shippingAddress 只读属性返回一个 PaymentAddress 对象，该对象包含用户提供的送货地址。

trans-unit.source: The shippingOption read-only attribute of the PaymentRequest interface returns either the id of a selected shipping option, null (if no shipping option was set to be selected) or a shipping option selected by the user. It is initially null by when no "selected" shipping options are provided.
trans-unit.target: PaymentRequest 接口的 shippingOption 只读属性返回所选送货选项的ID，null（如果未设置要选择的送货选项）或用户选择的送货选项。最初，如果没有提供“选定的”运输选项，则为 null 。

trans-unit.source: The shippingOption read-only property of the PaymentRequest interface returns the ID attribute of the shipping option selected by the user. This option is only present when the requestShipping option is set to true in the PaymentOptions object passed to the PaymentRequest constructor.
trans-unit.target: PaymentRequest 接口的 shippingOption 只读属性返回用户选择的送货选项的ID属性。仅当传递给 PaymentRequest 构造函数的 PaymentOptions 对象中的 requestShipping 选项设置为 true 时，此选项才存在。

trans-unit.source: The shippingType read-only property of the PaymentRequest interface returns one of "shipping", "delivery", "pickup", or null if one was not provided by the constructor.
trans-unit.target: PaymentRequest 接口的 shippingType 只读属性返回 "shipping" ， "delivery" ， "pickup" ，如果构造函数未提供则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: The shippingaddresschange event doesn't receive the PaymentRequest object directly, so we fetch it from the target property of the event. If the request's shippingAddress has a value for country which isn't in the array validCountries, we generate the error.
trans-unit.target: 该 shippingaddresschange 事件不会收到 PaymentRequest 直接对象，所以我们从获取它 target 事件的性质。如果请求的 shippingAddress 的 country 值不在有效 validCountries 数组中，则会生成错误。

trans-unit.source: The shippingaddresschange event is triggered by a user-agent controlled interaction. If the address stored by the user agent changes at any time during a payment process, the event is triggered. To make sure an updated address is included when sending payment information to the server, you should add event listeners for a PaymentRequest object after instantiation, but before the call to show().
trans-unit.target: 所述 shippingaddresschange 事件是由用户代理控制的相互作用触发。如果用户代理存储的地址在付款过程中随时更改，则触发该事件。为了确保在向服务器发送付款信息时包括更新的地址，您应该在实例化之后但在调用 show() 之前为 PaymentRequest 对象添加事件侦听器。

trans-unit.source: The shippingoptionchange event is triggered by a user-agent controlled interaction. If the option stored by the user agent changes at any time during a payment process, the event is triggered. To make sure an updated option is included when sending payment information to the server, you should add event listeners for a PaymentRequest object after instantiation, but before the call to show().
trans-unit.target: 所述 shippingoptionchange 事件是由用户代理控制的相互作用触发。如果用户代理存储的选项在付款过程中随时更改，则触发该事件。为了确保在向服务器发送付款信息时包括更新的选项，您应该在实例化之后但在调用 show() 之前为 PaymentRequest 对象添加事件侦听器。

trans-unit.source: The show() method of the HTMLDialogElement interface displays the dialog modelessly, i.e. still allowing interaction with content outside of the dialog.
trans-unit.target: HTMLDialogElement 接口的 show() 方法以无模式显示对话框，即仍然允许与对话框外部的内容进行交互。

trans-unit.source: The showModal() method of the HTMLDialogElement interface displays the dialog as a modal, over the top of any other dialogs that might be present. It displays into the top layer, along with a ::backdrop pseudo-element. Interaction outside the dialog is blocked and the content outside it is rendered inert.
trans-unit.target: HTMLDialogElement 接口的 showModal() 方法将对话框显示为模态，显示在可能出现的任何其他对话框的上方。它显示在顶层以及:: backdrop伪元素。对话框外的交互将被阻止，并且对话框外的内容将变为惰性。

trans-unit.source: The showNotification() method of the ServiceWorkerRegistration interface creates a notification on an active service worker.
trans-unit.target: ServiceWorkerRegistration 接口的 showNotification() 方法在活动的服务工作程序上创建通知。

trans-unit.source: The signal read-only property of the AbortController interface returns an AbortSignal object instance, which can be used to communicate with/abort a DOM request as desired.
trans-unit.target: AbortController 接口的 signal 只读属性返回一个 AbortSignal 对象实例，该实例可用于根据需要与DOM请求通信/中止该请求。

trans-unit.source: The silent read-only property of the Notification interface specifies whether the notification should be silent, i.e. no sounds or vibrations should be issued, regardless of the device settings. This is specified in the renotify option of the Notification() constructor.
trans-unit.target: Notification 接口的 silent 只读属性指定通知是否应为静音，即无论设备设置如何，都不应发出声音或振动。这是在 Notification() 构造函数的 renotify 选项中指定的。

trans-unit.source: The sittingToStandingTransform read-only property of the VRStageParameters interface contains a matrix that transforms the sitting-space view matrices of VRFrameData to standing-space.
trans-unit.target: VRStageParameters 接口的 sittingToStandingTransform 只读属性包含一个矩阵，该矩阵将 VRFrameData 的就座空间视图矩阵转换为就座空间。

trans-unit.source: The size() method of the CountQueuingStrategy interface always returns 1, so that the total queue size is a count of the number of chunks in the queue.
trans-unit.target: CountQueuingStrategy 接口的 size() 方法始终返回 1 ，因此总队列大小是队列中块数的计数。

trans-unit.source: The size() method of the ByteLengthQueueingStrategy interface returns the given chunk’s byteLength property.
trans-unit.target: ByteLengthQueueingStrategy 接口的 size() 方法返回给定块的 byteLength 属性。

trans-unit.source: The size attribute of the return value corresponds to the length of the array for uniforms declared as arrays. Otherwise, it is 1 (this includes interface blocks instanced with arrays).
trans-unit.target: 返回值的 size 属性对应于声明为数组的制服的数组长度。否则，它为1（这包括用数组实例化的接口块）。

trans-unit.source: The size read-only property of the KeyboardLayoutMap interface returns the number of elements in the map.
trans-unit.target: KeyboardLayoutMap 接口的 size 只读属性返回映射中的元素数。

trans-unit.source: The size read-only property of the MediaKeyStatusMap interface returns the number of key/value paIrs in the status map.
trans-unit.target: MediaKeyStatusMap 接口的 size 只读属性返回状态图中的键/值对象数。

trans-unit.source: The size read-only property of the StylePropertyMapReadOnly interface returns an unsinged long integer containing the size of the StylePropertyMapReadOnly object.
trans-unit.target: StylePropertyMapReadOnly 接口的 size 只读属性返回一个不带整数的长整数，其中包含 StylePropertyMapReadOnly 对象的大小。

trans-unit.source: The sizeX read-only property of the VRStageParameters interface
trans-unit.target: VRStageParameters 接口的 sizeX 只读属性

trans-unit.source: The sizeY read-only property of the VRStageParameters interface
trans-unit.target: VRStageParameters 接口的 sizeY 只读属性

trans-unit.source: The sliCount property of the RTCRtpStreamStats dictionary indicates how many Slice Loss Indication (SLI) packets were received by the sender. An SLI packet is used by a decoder to let the encoder know that it's detected corruption of one or more consecutive macroblocks in the received media.
trans-unit.target: RTCRtpStreamStats 词典的 sliCount 属性指示发送方接收了多少个分片丢失指示（SLI）数据包。SLI数据包由解码器用来使编码器知道它检测到接收到的媒体中一个或多个连续宏块的损坏。

trans-unit.source: The slot property of the Element interface returns the name of the shadow DOM slot the element is inserted in.
trans-unit.target: Element 接口的 slot 属性返回插入元素的影子DOM插槽的名称。

trans-unit.source: The smoothingTimeConstant property of the AnalyserNode interface is a double value representing the averaging constant with the last analysis frame. It's basically an average between the current buffer and the last buffer the AnalyserNode processed, and results in a much smoother set of value changes over time.
trans-unit.target: AnalyserNode 接口的 smoothingTimeConstant 属性是一个双精度值，代表最后一个分析帧的平均常数。它基本上是当前缓冲区和 AnalyserNode 处理的最后一个缓冲区之间的平均值，并且会导致随着时间的推移值变化更加平滑。

trans-unit.source: The sortingCode read-only property of the PaymentAddress interface returns a string containing a postal sorting code such as is used in France.
trans-unit.target: PaymentAddress 接口的 sortingCode 只读属性返回一个字符串，该字符串包含邮政分类码，例如在法国使用的。

trans-unit.source: The source read-only property of the IDBCursor interface returns the IDBObjectStore or IDBIndex that the cursor is iterating over. This function never returns null or throws an exception, even if the cursor is currently being iterated, has iterated past its end, or its transaction is not active.
trans-unit.target: IDBCursor 接口的 source 只读属性返回游标正在其上进行迭代的 IDBObjectStore 或 IDBIndex 。此函数永远不会返回null或引发异常，即使当前正在对游标进行迭代，经过游标的迭代，或者其事务未处于活动状态也是如此。

trans-unit.source: The source read-only property of the IDBRequest interface returns the source of the request, such as an Index or an object store. If no source exists (such as when calling indexedDB.open), it returns null.
trans-unit.target: IDBRequest 接口的 source 只读属性返回请求的源，例如索引或对象存储。如果不存在任何源（例如调用 indexedDB.open 时），则返回null。

trans-unit.source: The spacing keyword.
trans-unit.target: 该 spacing 关键字。

trans-unit.source: The spacingAndGlyphs keyword.
trans-unit.target: 该 spacingAndGlyphs 关键字。

trans-unit.source: The span property is now an unsigned long.
trans-unit.target: 该 span 属性现在是一个 unsigned long 。

trans-unit.source: The speaking read-only property of the SpeechSynthesis interface is a Boolean that returns true if an utterance is currently in the process of being spoken — even if SpeechSynthesis is in a paused state.
trans-unit.target: SpeechSynthesis 接口的 speaking 只读属性是一个 Boolean ，如果当前正在说出语音，则返回 true ，即使 SpeechSynthesis 处于 paused 状态也是如此。

trans-unit.source: The speechSynthesis read-only property of the Window object returns a SpeechSynthesis object, which is the entry point into using Web Speech API speech synthesis functionality.
trans-unit.target: Window对象的 speechSynthesis 只读属性返回 SpeechSynthesis 对象，该对象是使用Web Speech API语音合成功能的入口点。

trans-unit.source: The src property of the constructed HTMLAudioElement.
trans-unit.target: 构造的 HTMLAudioElement 的 src 属性。

trans-unit.source: The srcObject property of the HTMLMediaElement interface sets or returns the object which serves as the source of the media associated with the HTMLMediaElement. The object can be a MediaStream, a MediaSource, a Blob, or a File (which inherits from Blob).
trans-unit.target: HTMLMediaElement 接口的 srcObject 属性设置或返回用作与 HTMLMediaElement 关联的媒体源的对象。该对象可以是 MediaStream ， MediaSource ， Blob 或 File （从 Blob 继承）。

trans-unit.source: The start() method of the AudioBufferSourceNode Interface is used to schedule playback of the audio data contained in the buffer, or to begin playback immediately.
trans-unit.target: AudioBufferSourceNode 接口的 start() 方法用于安排缓冲区中包含的音频数据的播放，或立即开始播放。

trans-unit.source: The start() method on AudioScheduledSourceNode schedules a sound to begin playback at the specified time. If no time is specified, then the sound begins playing immediately.
trans-unit.target: AudioScheduledSourceNode 上的 start() 方法计划声音在指定时间开始播放。如果未指定时间，则声音立即开始播放。

trans-unit.source: The start() property of the PresentationRequest interface returns a Promise that resolves with a PresentationConnection after the user agent prompts the user to select a display and grant permission to use that display.
trans-unit.target: PresentationRequest 接口的 start() 属性返回一个 Promise ，该Promise在用户代理提示用户选择显示并授予使用该显示的权限后，通过 PresentationConnection 进行解析。

trans-unit.source: The start event is thrown as a result of the MediaRecorder.start() method being invoked. At this point, the data starts being gathered into a Blob.
trans-unit.target: 由于调用 MediaRecorder.start() 方法而引发了 start 事件。此时，数据开始收集到 Blob 中。

trans-unit.source: The start method activates one of the sensors based on Sensor.
trans-unit.target: 所述 start 方法激活基于所述传感器中的一个 Sensor 。

trans-unit.source: The start method of the OscillatorNode interface specifies the exact time to start playing the tone. Its parameter is optional and default to 0.
trans-unit.target: OscillatorNode 接口的 start 方法指定开始播放音调的确切时间。它的参数是可选的，默认为 0 。

trans-unit.source: The startContainer property of the StaticRange interface returns the start Node for the range.
trans-unit.target: StaticRange 接口的 startContainer 属性返回范围的起始 Node 。

trans-unit.source: The startMessages() method of the ServiceWorkerContainer interface explicitly starts the flow of messages being dispatched from a service worker to pages under its control (e.g. sent via Client.postMessage()). Can be used to avoid race conditions created when a service worker tries to post a message to a page before that page has actually finished loading an ServiceWorkerContainer.onmessage handler to process them..
trans-unit.target: ServiceWorkerContainer 接口的 startMessages() 方法显式启动从服务工作人员调度到其控制下的页面的消息流（例如，通过 Client.postMessage() 发送）。可用于避免服务工作者尝试在页面实际完成加载 ServiceWorkerContainer.onmessage 处理程序之前将消息发布到该页面时创建的竞争条件。

trans-unit.source: The startOffset property of the StaticRange interface returns the offset into the start node of the range's start position.
trans-unit.target: StaticRange 接口的 startOffset 属性将偏移量返回到范围起始位置的起始节点。

trans-unit.source: The startRecording() function handles starting the recording process:
trans-unit.target: 所述 startRecording() 函数处理开始记录过程：

trans-unit.source: The startRendering() method of the OfflineAudioContext Interface starts rendering the audio graph, taking into account the current connections and the current scheduled changes.
trans-unit.target: 考虑到当前连接和当前计划的更改， OfflineAudioContext 接口的 startRendering() 方法开始呈现音频图。

trans-unit.source: The startTime property returns the first recorded timestamp of the performance entry.
trans-unit.target: 在 startTime 属性返回第一个记录 timestamp 的的 performance entry 。

trans-unit.source: The startVideo() method handles setting up and starting the video stream.
trans-unit.target: 所述 startVideo() 方法处理设置和开始视频流。

trans-unit.source: The startup() function is run when the page has finished loading, courtesy of window.addEventListener(). This function's job is to request access to the user's webcam, initialize the output <img> to a default state, and to establish the event listeners needed to receive each frame of video from the camera and react when the button is clicked to capture an image.
trans-unit.target: 在 startup() 函数在运行时的页面加载完成后，礼貌 window.addEventListener() 。该功能的工作是请求访问用户的网络摄像头，将输出 <img> 初始化为默认状态，并建立事件侦听器，以接收来自摄像机的每一帧视频，并在单击按钮以捕获图像时做出反应。

trans-unit.source: The state read-only property of the BaseAudioContext interface returns the current state of the AudioContext.
trans-unit.target: BaseAudioContext 接口的 state 只读属性返回 AudioContext 的当前状态。

trans-unit.source: The state read-only property of the ServiceWorker interface returns a string representing the current state of the service worker. It can be one of the following values: installing, installed,activating, activated, or redundant.
trans-unit.target: ServiceWorker 接口的 state 只读属性返回一个字符串，该字符串表示服务工作者的当前状态。它可以是以下值之一： installing ， installed, activating ， activated 或 redundant 。

trans-unit.source: The status read-only property of the Response interface contains the status code of the response (e.g., 200 for a success).
trans-unit.target: Response 接口的 status 只读属性包含响应的状态代码（例如 200 表示成功）。

trans-unit.source: The statusMessage property can contain a platform dependent string with details of an event. This can occur, for example, if the webglcontextcreationerror event is fired.
trans-unit.target: 该 statusMessage 属性可以包含一个平台相关的字符串与事件的细节。例如，如果触发了 webglcontextcreationerror 事件，则可能发生这种情况。

trans-unit.source: The step read-only property of the MediaSettingsRange interface returns the minimum difference between consecutive values of the settings range.
trans-unit.target: MediaSettingsRange 接口的 step 只读属性返回设置范围的连续值之间的最小差异。

trans-unit.source: The stop() function simply stops the input media:
trans-unit.target: 将 stop() 函数简单地停止输入媒体：

trans-unit.source: The stop() method in the RTCRtpTransceiver interface permanently stops the transceiver by stopping both the associated RTCRtpSender and RTCRtpReceiver. Once stopped, the transceiver's stopped property will return true.
trans-unit.target: RTCRtpTransceiver 接口中的 stop() 方法通过停止关联的 RTCRtpSender 和 RTCRtpReceiver 来永久停止收发器。一旦停止，收发器的 stopped 属性将返回 true 。

trans-unit.source: The stop() method on AudioScheduledSourceNode schedules a sound to cease playback at the specified time. If no time is specified, then the sound stops playing immediately.
trans-unit.target: AudioScheduledSourceNode 上的 stop() 方法安排声音以在指定时间停止播放。如果未指定时间，则声音会立即停止播放。

trans-unit.source: The stop event is thrown either as a result of the MediaRecorder.stop() method being invoked, or when the media stream being captured ends. In each case, the stop event is preceded by a dataavailable event, making the Blob captured up to that point available for you to use in your application.
trans-unit.target: 由于调用 MediaRecorder.stop() 方法，或者捕获的媒体流结束时，将引发 stop 事件。在每种情况下， stop 事件之前都有一个 dataavailable 事件，这使捕获到该点的 Blob 可供您在应用程序中使用。

trans-unit.source: The stop method of the OscillatorNode interface specifies the time to stop playing the tone. Its parameter is optional and defaults to 0.
trans-unit.target: OscillatorNode 接口的 stop 方法指定停止播放声音的时间。它的参数是可选的，默认为 0 。

trans-unit.source: The stop method of the Sensor interface deactivates the current sensor.
trans-unit.target: Sensor 界面的 stop 方法会禁用当前传感器。

trans-unit.source: The storage event is fired on a document's Window object when a storage area changes.
trans-unit.target: 当存储区域更改时，将在文档的 Window 对象上触发该 storage 事件。

trans-unit.source: The storageQuota property of the Navigator interface of the Quota Management API provides means to query and request storage usage and quota information. You can get a reference to this interface using Navigator.storageQuota.
trans-unit.target: 配额管理API的 Navigator 界面的 storageQuota 属性提供查询和请求存储使用情况和配额信息的方法。您可以使用 Navigator.storageQuota 对此接口进行引用。

trans-unit.source: The store() method of the CredentialsContainer stores a set of credentials for the user inside a Credential instance, returning this in a Promise.
trans-unit.target: CredentialsContainer 的 store() 方法将用户的一组凭据存储在 Credential 实例中，并在 Promise 中返回该凭据。

trans-unit.source: The stream property of the AudioContext interface represents a MediaStream containing a single AudioMediaStreamTrack with the same number of channels as the node itself.
trans-unit.target: AudioContext 接口的 stream 属性表示一个 MediaStream ，该MediaStream包含单个 AudioMediaStreamTrack ，其通道数量与节点本身相同。

trans-unit.source: The strict value will prevent the cookie from being sent by the browser to the target site in all cross-site browsing context, even when following a regular link.
trans-unit.target: 在 strict 值将会阻止该cookie在所有跨站点浏览器上下文浏览器发送到目标站点，以下常规链接时也是如此。

trans-unit.source: The strokeRect() method draws a stroked rectangle whose starting point is at (x, y) and whose size is specified by width and height.

trans-unit.source: The suspend() method of the AudioContext Interface suspends the progression of time in the audio context, temporarily halting audio hardware access and reducing CPU/battery usage in the process — this is useful if you want an application to power down the audio hardware when it will not be using an audio context for a while.

trans-unit.source: The transaction() function takes two arguments (though one is optional) and returns a transaction object. You can pass an empty array if you want the transaction to span all object stores, but don't do it because the spec says an empty array should generate an InvalidAccessError. trans-unit.source: The window.navigator.appVersion, window.navigator.appName and window.navigator.userAgent properties have been used in "browser sniffing" code: scripts that attempt to find out what kind of browser you are using and adjust pages accordingly. trans-unit.target: 该 RTCIceCandidate 接口的只读 relatedAddress 属性是表示一个字符串相关的地址继电器或反射候选的。如果候选对象是主机候选对象（也就是说，其 ip 实际上是远程对等方的真实IP地址），则 relatedAddress 为 null 。
